16
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:14,910
For years?

17
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:16,660
Haven't we just met recently?

18
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:23,470
- Come.
- Let's eat.

19
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:25,470
When's your wedding?

20
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:26,900
I'll definitely prepare a big gift.

21
00:02:28,310 --> 00:02:29,190
We...

22
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:31,310
Almost.

23
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:33,980
Right. We've prepared everything.

24
00:02:33,980 --> 00:02:34,630
Soon.

25
00:02:34,820 --> 00:02:35,820
Dig in.

26
00:02:38,030 --> 00:02:39,260
How about we watch a movie?

27
00:02:40,510 --> 00:02:41,660
As long as you have time.

28
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:42,920
What movie do you want to watch?

29
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:44,380
Anything.

30
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:45,190
Anything?

31
00:02:45,820 --> 00:02:46,630
All right.

