(Bye, Su Zihao.)

47
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,540
(Bye, Tong Leyi.)

48
00:04:08,790 --> 00:04:09,580
Ms. Dai.

49
00:04:12,820 --> 00:04:14,070
Why haven't you left yet?

50
00:04:15,100 --> 00:04:16,430
Please sign this for me.

51
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:19,330
(Resignation Letter)
This is my resignation letter.

52
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:23,700
Zhou.

53
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:25,380
Zihao is here.

54
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:28,460
Zihao, have a seat.

55
00:04:28,460 --> 00:04:29,510
I'm making chili oil.

56
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:31,110
Is there something wrong

57
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:32,340
with Sansan's enrollment?

58
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:34,550
No, everything's going well.

59
00:04:34,550 --> 00:04:35,140
Really?

60
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:36,110
Yes.

61
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:36,990
Thank you.

62
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:37,900
Well.

63
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:40,260
You did me such a big favor.

64
00:04:40,670 --> 00:04:42,110
I'll surely repay you handsomely.

65
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:43,990
Seriously?

66
00:04:43,990 --> 00:04:45,110
Why are you always thinking

67
00:04:45,110 --> 00:04:46,460
about these worldly matters?

68
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:48,310
Where did the old you go?

69
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:50,580
What is that?

70
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,430
The old me?

71
00:04:52,820 --> 00:04:54,550
You were a promising man.

72
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:58,190
Why do you want to quit?

73
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:00,510
You're jumping ship?

74
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:02,140
No, I'm not.

75
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:03,510
I'm just too tired from work.

76
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:04,820
You want an easy life?

77
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:07,460
Then why even come to work?

78
00:05:07,460 --> 00:05:08,700
You could've done that earlier.

79
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:10,700
Guess why I come to work.

80
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:12,670
Do you remember

81
00:05:12,670 --> 00:05:13,870
I said

82
00:05:14,380 --> 00:05:15,870
I've known you for a long time?

83
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:17,670
That's not quite right.

84
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:19,550
To be accurate,

85
00:05:20,550 --> 00:05:22,340
I know the old you.

86
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:24,750
What do you mean?

87
00:05:27,260 --> 00:05:30,110
(Scandalous Couple)
I know the story between Dai Daji and you.

88
00:05:30,990 --> 00:05:32,310
About you and Zhou Shui,

89
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,340
I know everything about it.

90
00:05:52,780 --> 00:05:53,580
Thank you.

91
00:05:54,650 --> 00:05:56,430
You went through every pitfall
ahead of me.

92
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,140
I remember it all.

93
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:01,260
To cherish my life,

94
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:02,440
I must stay away from love.

95
00:06:08,550 --> 00:06:10,190
But what you saw in those videos

96
00:06:11,070 --> 00:06:12,340
isn't the whole story.

97
00:06:14,020 --> 00:06:15,380
We were apart,

98
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:17,380
but that wasn't the end.

99
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,380
We got back together afterward.

100
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,430
We were together

101
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:23,820
for ten years.

102
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,070
Do you want to know
what happened after that?

103
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:29,020
Do you want to know

104
00:06:29,110 --> 00:06:30,780
how it ended?

