121
00:07:57,820 --> 00:07:59,550
(a completely different life)

122
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:02,460
(with the baby.)

123
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:08,510
(At that time, I didn't know)

124
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:11,630
(Zhou Shui and I wouldn't
come back together)

125
00:08:12,430 --> 00:08:13,820
(after leaving Beijing.)

126
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:26,510
(Haikou Airport)
So hot.

127
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:29,860
Hi.

128
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:30,780
Director Zhou?

129
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:31,750
Yes. Zhou Shui.

130
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:32,910
Hello.

131
00:08:32,910 --> 00:08:33,390
Hi.

132
00:08:33,550 --> 00:08:35,070
I'm the production manager.

133
00:08:35,070 --> 00:08:35,950
Chen Biao.

134
00:08:35,950 --> 00:08:37,150
Just call me Biao.

135
00:08:37,150 --> 00:08:38,340
- Biao.
- Welcome to Hainan.

136
00:08:39,580 --> 00:08:40,430
And this is...

137
00:08:40,820 --> 00:08:41,980
Also a director of this movie.

138
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:42,980
I'm Dai Daji.

139
00:08:44,620 --> 00:08:45,460
Two directors?

140
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:46,340
- Yeah.
- Right.

141
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:48,790
Director Dai and I
will co-direct this movie.

142
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:50,030
Didn't Man tell you about this?

143
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:54,670
Let's get in the car first.

144
00:08:57,191 --> 00:08:57,950
I've visited

145
00:08:57,950 --> 00:09:00,030
the main settings these past few days.

146
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:01,550
I've come up with plans.

147
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:02,910
Take a look at this.

148
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:05,190
This is the real dorm.

149
00:09:05,220 --> 00:09:05,910
Overall,

150
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:07,580
it's too old.

151
00:09:07,670 --> 00:09:09,270
Plus, it's dirty, messy, and rundown.

152
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:10,460
The space is cramped.

153
00:09:10,460 --> 00:09:11,460
It'll be inconvenient

154
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:12,220
for everyone

155
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:13,620
to work there.

156
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:15,460
Now, look at this one.

157
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:18,620
This is the ideal dorm.

158
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:19,910
The atmosphere

159
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,270
and the layout

160
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:22,860
are easier to work with.

161
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:25,980
Since the dorm is our main set,

162
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:27,500
I suggest we build a set.

163
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:29,030
Of course, we have to build a set.

164
00:09:29,310 --> 00:09:31,340
Anyway, just as we discussed
in the meeting.

165
00:09:31,430 --> 00:09:32,460
Xiaozhi,

166
00:09:32,460 --> 00:09:33,550
you deal with the design...

167
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:34,670
Ms. Chao has arrived.

168
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:35,860
Ms. Chao.

169
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:37,820
Hi, Ms. Chao.

170
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:41,500
Sit.

171
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:55,430
I heard someone wants to build a set?

172
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:57,550
Director Zhou.

173
00:09:58,030 --> 00:10:00,070
He said the dorm

174
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:01,310
is one of our main sets,

175
00:10:01,310 --> 00:10:03,310
so he wanted to build a set.

176
00:10:04,580 --> 00:10:05,390
It was me.

177
00:10:05,430 --> 00:10:06,390
What's the budget?

178
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:08,270
Around 800,000.

179
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:12,500
Just shoot with a real dorm, okay?

180
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:13,860
Don't waste the budget.

181
00:10:14,070 --> 00:10:14,500
Sure.

182
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:15,220
Ms. Chao,

183
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:18,270
but the real dorm

184
00:10:18,270 --> 00:10:19,150
is cramped

185
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,500
and dark.

186
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:22,740
It'll look bad on camera.

187
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:23,620
Excuse me.

188
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,910
Do you have more experience than me?

189
00:10:26,740 --> 00:10:28,390
I don't think it necessary.

190
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:28,980
Ms. Chao,

191
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:31,070
it's not about experience.

192
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:32,030
You told us

193
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:33,620
that you need a romantic vibe

194
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:34,740
for this scene.

195
00:10:35,190 --> 00:10:35,620
But if...

196
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:36,740
Tell me.

197
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:39,270
If we spend this money,

198
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:41,700
can we generate another
100 million earnings?

199
00:10:42,460 --> 00:10:43,270
100 million?

200
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:44,860
Who can guarantee that?

201
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:45,430
Right.

202
00:10:45,460 --> 00:10:47,700
If you spend the 800,000

203
00:10:47,700 --> 00:10:49,430
and it doesn't generate any profit,

204
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,330
are you going to
take responsibility for that?

205
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:54,860
Well, that's final.

206
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:56,270
We'll use a real dorm.

207
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:56,860
Deal.

208
00:10:57,170 --> 00:10:58,070
That's great, Ms. Chao.

209
00:10:58,070 --> 00:10:59,950
That's exactly what we thought.

210
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:01,150
Come, Xiaozhi.

211
00:11:01,150 --> 00:11:02,340
Show Ms. Chao the proposal.

212
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:02,980
Here you go.

213
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:05,670
This is the campus we found.

214
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:07,950
Both Xiaozhi and I agreed

215
00:11:07,950 --> 00:11:09,390
that live-action filming is the best.

216
00:11:09,740 --> 00:11:10,550
Yeah. Look at this.

217
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:11,790
The area is open.

218
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:13,790
Right? The cameraman can stand here.

219
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:14,460
Right.

220
00:11:14,460 --> 00:11:16,030
Besides, the sunlight is strong.

221
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:17,230
You thought of everything.

222
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:19,190
The money we save

223
00:11:19,190 --> 00:11:21,430
can be used to improve the set.

224
00:11:26,340 --> 00:11:26,820
Let's go.

225
00:11:27,298 --> 00:11:29,705
Ms. Chao, Xiaozhi and I discussed it.

226
00:11:29,705 --> 00:11:31,700
Most of the budget has been used.

227
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:34,316
The space is square
and lacks visual appeal.

228
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:36,847
Most importantly, the road across that.

229
00:11:36,847 --> 00:11:38,860
- It's a perfect filming spot.
- Exactly.

230
00:11:39,109 --> 00:11:39,996
Scroll up.

231
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:45,790
Right here.

232
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:49,690
Well.

233
00:11:49,690 --> 00:11:51,270
I didn't know there would be two of you,

234
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:52,790
so I only prepared one single bed.

235
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:55,380
But the sheets and blanket are all new.

236
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:56,460
Once the whole crew arrives,

237
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:57,700
I'll bring in another bed.

238
00:11:58,430 --> 00:12:00,390
Does the bed even reach one meter?

239
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:02,950
This is a standard
1.5 meters by 1 meter.

240
00:12:04,550 --> 00:12:05,500
1.5 meters long?

241
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:06,980
Right. The place is fine, right?

242
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,390
Young directors

243
00:12:08,390 --> 00:12:09,310
should learn to adapt.

244
00:12:09,310 --> 00:12:10,980
You should learn from Ms. Chao.

245
00:12:11,070 --> 00:12:12,070
You're right.

246
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:13,550
All right.

247
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:14,980
Which room is she in?

248
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:16,310
I'll go seek her guidance later.

249
00:12:16,310 --> 00:12:18,390
Ms. Chao is staying
at Hilton in the city.

250
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:20,150
It's getting late.

251
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,500
You must be tired from the trip.

252
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:22,460
Rest up.

253
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:22,980
Well.

254
00:12:22,980 --> 00:12:23,950
Let me through.

255
00:12:23,980 --> 00:12:25,500
Make way.

256
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:26,430
Move the luggage back.

257
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:29,310
Call me if anything comes up.

258
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:34,580
She's changing the script

259
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:37,220
however she wants.

260
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:40,190
Look at what we're facing.

261
00:12:40,310 --> 00:12:41,670
What more does she want from us?

262
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:44,980
The place isn't great,

263
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:47,500
but we've lived in worse,

264
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,220
haven't we?

265
00:12:48,310 --> 00:12:49,460
It's not about this place.

266
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:50,790
That's nothing.

267
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:51,940
It's the set.

268
00:12:51,940 --> 00:12:53,500
She won't even give us money for that.

269
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:54,670
How are we supposed to shoot?

270
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:03,220
Back when we were at Shendu,

271
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:05,100
we only had 100 yuan.

272
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,430
We made films with just 100 yuan.

273
00:13:07,430 --> 00:13:08,700
We can do anything!

274
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:13,550
You can tolerate anything.

275
00:13:15,100 --> 00:13:16,220
We're the directors.

276
00:13:17,460 --> 00:13:19,950
Once we start filming,

277
00:13:20,620 --> 00:13:22,430
we call the shots.

278
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:25,270
Right?

279
00:13:29,220 --> 00:13:30,700
I'm enduring it!

280
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:46,670
All right.

281
00:13:48,740 --> 00:13:49,670
I feel better now.

282
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:52,220
Zhou Shui.

283
00:13:52,220 --> 00:13:53,620
Director Zhou.

284
00:13:53,790 --> 00:13:54,430
Ms. Chao

285
00:13:54,430 --> 00:13:56,150
has assigned you an executive director.

286
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:57,700
He's quite famous,

287
00:13:57,700 --> 00:13:59,100
so watch your attitude.

288
